title: Mahakaal
subTitle: Prof. Ajoy Mukherjee and his wife testify against criminal Digbijay, leading to unforeseen consequences. Their son Joy becomes entangled in a dangerous web of deceit.

title: Bornoporichoy
subTitle: Dhananjoy, a police detective, goes on a desperate lookout for Arko, a man who murders people, taking inspiration from the five elements- Earth, Water, Wind, Sky, and Fire.

subTitle: Mainadevi approaches Narayan and requests him to marry Parvati, and he accepts her proposal. Narayan impersonates Lord Shiva to meet Parvati.

subTitle: Two rival groups compete against each other in all aspects of their college life. However, the only obstruction to their growing enmity is their extremely disciplined dean.

title: Maan Maryada
subTitle: Yogesh, a selfless man, takes care and raises his two step-brothers, a step-sister and an orphan boy. However, when things go south and he becomes bankrupt, his step-siblings abandon him.

title: Sejo Bou
subTitle: A poor man falls in love with a girl belonging to a wealthy family. In an attempt to separate them, the man is sent abroad. However, the couple's destiny intervenes, striving to bring them together.

title: Hullor

subTitle: While running away from an arranged marriage, Rupa meets Sonu, a mechanic who changes her life forever.

title: Khiladi
subTitle: Two families of opposing faiths are in a long-standing rivalry over land and past wounds. However, one man vows to reunite them by disguising himself as a Hindu person.

title: Byomkesh Gotro
subTitle: A young womanizer seeks help from a detective, fearing for his life, but is murdered before their meeting, meanwhile investigation uncovers his family's dark secrets in a hill station.

subTitle: Parvati realises Narayan's deceit. She confronts him to declare his true identity and refuses to marry. Mainadevi becomes anxious when Parvati transforms into Goddess Adishakti.

subTitle: When Bijoy and Rani's squabble turns into a blossoming love, her mother opposes their union. With their young romance facing the threat of family disapproval, they must find a way to turn it around.

subTitle: After being accused and jailed an honest man learns about his twin brother who is an humble policeman and then, he disguises as a police inspector to catch the culprits and find his uncle who is lost.

title: Pratibad
subTitle: A fierce fighter against injustice strives to help his middle-class family make ends meet. His dedication lands him a job as a police officer, where he tackles large-scale problems with determination.

title: Fidaa
subTitle: Ishaan and Khushi fall in love despite their differing perspectives on romance and life. However, their egos and misunderstandings threaten to ruin their relationship.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: After learning about Parvati's true identity, Mainadevi realises her mistake. Ganga implores Mainadevi to grant permission for the wedding of Lord Shiva and Parvati.

subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

subTitle: Arjun leaves the village for to become an IPS officer. Along with his friend Deepak, he plans to meet his family but while coming back, they get into an accident.

title: Greftaar
